}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== This device is sold under the Aluratek and Zalip brands.
"11340Y20CM00003A1" is silkscreened on the board. There is a '''TI''' PCI1510 7A85A8L7W on board for the CardBus controller.
The power adapter included with the device is a '''JENTEC''' AF1805-B (5V, 3A). ID/OD/Len measurements are approximate.
